sequenceDiagram
    participant App as PaultApp
    participant MC as ModelContainer
    participant AD as AppDelegate
    participant MB as Menu Bar
    participant HK as Hotkey Manager

    App->>MC: Create SwiftData container
    App->>AD: Assign model container
    App->>AD: applicationDidFinishLaunching
    AD->>MB: Setup status item + popover
    AD->>HK: Register global hotkey
